---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="can’t sleep? how to fix your sleep naturally"
  description="simple steps to fix sleep problems and restore natural rhythm."
>
  <section class="page-hero section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">guide</p>
      <h1>can’t sleep? here’s how to fix it naturally</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        if you can’t fall asleep, wake up tired, or feel wired at night, your sleep rhythm is likely out of sync.
      </p>
      <p class="lead">
        fix the rhythm, and sleep starts to fix itself.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>start with rhythm</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>wake up at the same time every day</p>
          <p>go outside within 30–60 minutes</p>
          <p>keep your schedule consistent</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>reduce night disruption</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>dim lights after sunset</p>
          <p>limit screens 60–90 minutes before bed</p>
          <p>avoid heavy stimulation at night</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">optional tool</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">sleep</span>
        </div>
        <h2>reduce blue light at night</h2>
        <p>
          if you’re using screens at night, blue light blocking glasses can help reduce stimulation
          and make it easier to wind down.
        </p>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>wear them 60–90 minutes before bed</p>
          <p>helps support natural melatonin production</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/recommendations/blue-light-glasses" class="button">view recommended option</a>
        <p class="panel-kicker" style="margin-top: 0.4rem;">
          or browse all <a href="/recommendations">recommended tools</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>support the body</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>move during the day</p>
          <p>eat consistent meals</p>
          <p>avoid late caffeine spikes</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">optional tool</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">sleep</span>
        </div>
        <h2>support relaxation at night</h2>
        <p>
          magnesium can help calm the nervous system and make it easier to relax before sleep,
          especially if you feel tense or restless at night.
        </p>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>supports deeper sleep</p>
          <p>helps reduce tension</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/recommendations/magnesium" class="button">view recommended option</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section accent-section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>what not to do</h2>

      <div class="content-block">
        <p>trying to force sleep</p>
        <p>random sleep schedules</p>
        <p>bright screens in the dark</p>
        <p>lying awake with high stimulation</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">checklist</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">fix</span>
        </div>
        <h2>simple sleep reset checklist</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>wake at the same time daily</p>
          <p>get sunlight early every day</p>
          <p>dim lights at night</p>
          <p>limit screens before bed</p>
          <p>build a consistent rhythm</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">related</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">next</span>
        </div>
        <h2>go deeper</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p><a href="/best-sleep-routine">build a consistent sleep routine</a></p>
          <p><a href="/best-morning-routine">fix your mornings to fix your nights</a></p>
          <p><a href="/why-you-feel-tired-all-the-time">understand low energy</a></p>
          <p><a href="/start-here">follow the full baseline system</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">free guide</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">system</span>
        </div>
        <h2>build your full daily baseline</h2>

        <form class="hero-actions" action="/start-here" method="GET">
          <input
            class="email-input"
            type="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="your email"
            required
          />
          <button class="button primary-cta" type="submit">
            get the guide
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="two-panel-grid">
        <a href="/best-sleep-routine" class="y2k-panel feature-card">
          <p class="panel-kicker">previous</p>
          <h3>sleep routine</h3>
          <p>build a consistent nightly structure.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/start-here" class="y2k-panel feature-card">
          <p class="panel-kicker">next</p>
          <h3>start here</h3>
          <p>return to the full system and baseline path.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>